title: Google\Cloud\ErrorReporting\V1beta1\ListEventsRequest
name: ListEventsRequest
description:
Specifies a set of error events to return.

Generated from protobuf message google.devtools.clouderrorreporting.v1beta1.ListEventsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.project_name
params.description: Required. The resource name of the Google Cloud Platform project. Written as projects/{projectID}, where {projectID} is the Google Cloud Platform project ID. Example: projects/my-project-123.

params.name: data.group_id
params.description: Required. The group for which events shall be returned.

params.name: data.service_filter
params.description: Optional. List only ErrorGroups which belong to a service context that matches the filter. Data for all service contexts is returned if this field is not specified.

params.name: data.time_range
params.description: Optional. List only data for the given time range. If not set a default time range is used. The field time_range_begin in the response will specify the beginning of this time range.

params.name: data.page_size
params.description: Optional. The maximum number of results to return per response.

params.name: data.page_token
params.description: Optional. A next_page_token provided by a previous response.
